'''Charles J. Solomon''' is an [[United States|American]] [[Contract bridge|bridge]] player.

==Bridge accomplishments==

===Honors===

* ACBL Honorary Member 1961 <ref>[http://www.acbl.org/about-acbl/honorary-members/ ACBL Honorary Members]</ref>

